Information on how to retrieve your NHS number or fitness tracker password is described below.
&nbsp;
_Retrieve the NHS number:_
&nbsp;
You can find your National Health Service (NHS) number by following the instructions here: <https://www.nhs.uk/nhs-services/online-services/find-nhs-number/>
&nbsp;
_Find login details to the fitness tracking device:_
&nbsp;
Your fitness tracker login is the username and password you use to login and view all your recorded activity summaries on your fitness tracker. If you do not remember your login details, follow the device connection instructions provided within the study. During this process, select the “Forgot your password?” to reset your credentials and regain access to your account when you try to link your fitness tracker.
